    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant attention from its next owner. The exterior suffers from heavy oxidation, visible rust on the rocker panels, and several large dents, while the interior shows heavy wear with torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. Mechanically, the engine runs but has a persistent oil leak and the transmission shifts roughly, making it most suitable as a project car or a source for parts. It is recommended that any potential buyer brings a trailer, as its reliability for long-distance driving is not guaranteed.",
      "price": 6500.0,
