    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this impeccable specimen, preserved in showroom condition. This vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior that remains in pristine, original state. Meticulously maintained and subjected to a rigorous multi-point inspection, this automobile offers an uncompromising driving experience for the discerning enthusiast. It is rare to encounter a vehicle of this caliber on the secondary market; this is a definitive opportunity to acquire a masterpiece of automotive engineering.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You seriously have to see this absolute beauty! It\u2019s in such pristine, mint condition that you\u2019d honestly think it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this car from day one\u2014not a single scratch or smudge to be found, and it still has that brand-new smell! It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for its next adventure. I\u2019m so excited for someone to get behind the wheel and love it as much as I have. Grab this total gem while you can!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 1994 Mazda RX-7 FD, maintained to a peerless standard. This specimen features the iconic 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged rotary engine, delivering linear power delivery through the factory five-speed manual gearbox. The chassis remains exceptionally rigid, utilizing its original double-wishbone suspension and lightweight aluminum components for telepathic handling. Recent compression testing confirms optimal health across both rotors, ensuring the integrity of the apex seals and internal housings. Equipped with the factory Torsen limited-slip differential for precise torque vectoring, this FD retains its original aesthetics with zero aftermarket modifications. A rare opportunity for the purist seeking a mechanically flawless and thermally managed rotary legend.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Original paint. No mechanical or cosmetic defects. Full service records included. Clean title in hand.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, presented in absolute showroom condition. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections, while the interior remains as fresh as the day it left the factory, retaining that signature new-car scent. Meticulously garage-kept and strictly maintained by a single enthusiast owner, every mechanical component operates with precision. From the flawless alloy wheels to the pristine leather upholstery, no detail has been overlooked. This is an investment-grade example, complete with all original documentation and a full service history. If you are seeking perfection, this is the one.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle of exceptional caliber, maintained to the most exacting standards. This specimen remains in showroom condition, exhibiting a level of preservation that distinguishes it from the common market. Every surface, mechanical component, and interior appointment reflects a history of meticulous care. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle that retains its original luster and peak mechanical performance. We invite discerning buyers to inspect this benchmark of automotive excellence.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it\u2019s hard to believe this beauty is even pre-owned. It\u2019s been pampered since day one, kept tucked away in a garage, and still has that amazing fresh feel inside and out. Not a single scratch or dent to be found\u2014it\u2019s seriously in pristine shape! If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for a new adventure, you\u2019ve found it. I'd love for it to go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Come take a look, you definitely won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade E92 M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. This example features the high-revving S65 4.0L V8, delivering 414 hp through individual throttle bodies with a crisp 8,400 RPM redline. Mechanically flawless, the rod bearings and throttle actuators have been addressed preventatively with documented Blackstone oil reports. The chassis remains rigid, featuring an M-Variable differential and EDC-equipped suspension that retains factory-spec damping rates. The exterior boasts original paint with consistent depth readings across all panels, while the interior Novillo leather bolsters show zero compression or wear. Every VIN sticker is intact, and the underside is free of any fluid seepage or oxidation. This is a turn-key, investment-quality specimen for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
